Form990ScheduleLPartIV.DescriptionOfTransaction: Kevin Cooney is the Executive Director of Northern Counties Health Care, Inc. (NCHC), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. Transactions reported here are grant pass-through monies from the Association to NCHC ($29,485), and member services provided to NCHC ($20,628).

Edward George is the President/CEO of Manchester Community Health Center (MCHC), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. transactions reported here are federal grant pass through monies from the Association to MCHC ($30,430), and member services provided to MCHC ($13,424).

Ann Peters is the CEO of Lamprey Health Care, Inc. (LHC), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. transactions reported here are federal grant pass through monies from the Association to LHC ($122,639), and member services provided to LHC ($14,458).

Richard Silverberg is the Executive Director of Health First Family Care Center (HFFCC), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. transactions reported here are federal grant pass through monies from the Association to HFFCC ($25,172).

Helen Taft is the Executive Director of Families First Health and Support Center (FFHSC), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. transactions reported here are federal grant pass through monies from the Association to FFHSC ($44,858), and member services provided ($13,007) to FFHSC.

Edward Shanshala is the Executive Director of Ammonoosuc Community Health Services (ACHS), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. transactions reported here are federal grant pass through monies from the Association to ACHS.

Kevin Kelley is the CEO of COmmunity Health Center of Lamoille Valley (CHSLV), a member of Bi-State Primary Care Association, Inc. Transactions reported here are grant pass-through monies from the Association to CHSLV.
